'''Juan Daniel Alvez Ort<U+00ED>z''' (born August 21, 1983 in [[Montevideo, Uruguay]]) is a Uruguayan footballer currently playing for [[Liverpool F.C. (Montevideo)|Liverpool]] of the Primera Division in Uruguay.

==Teams==
* {{flagicon|URU}} [[Montevideo Wanderers F.C.|Montevideo Wanderers]] 2003-2008
* {{flagicon|URU}} [[Liverpool F.C. (Montevideo)|Liverpool]] 2008<U+2013>present

